---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { brand } from '../../config/brand';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Revenue Leak Audit | UHL Systems" description="Complete diagnostic of your revenue system. Find where your business is losing money - and get a prioritized roadmap to fix it. Starting at 1k - 2k." />
		<style>
			.section-heading {
				font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			}
			.hero-headline {
				font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.03em;
			}
			.cta-primary {
				background-color: var(--color-accent);
				color: var(--color-bg);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 14px 36px;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-primary:hover {
				box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.35);
				color: var(--color-bg);
			}
			.cta-ghost {
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 14px 36px;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-ghost:hover {
				border-color: var(--color-accent);
				color: var(--color-text);
			}
			.uhl-card {
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				background: var(--color-bg2);
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 40px 32px;
				transition: all 0.3s;
			}
			.uhl-card:hover {
				border-color: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.25);
				background: var(--color-bg3);
			}
			.content-width {
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.prose-width {
				max-width: 720px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
		</style>
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "FAQPage",
			"mainEntity": [
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "What exactly is a Revenue Leak Audit?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "A Revenue Leak Audit is a complete diagnostic of your business's revenue system. We analyze every stage - from traffic acquisition through to lifetime value - to identify where money is being left on the table. You receive a prioritized map of leaks, quick wins, and a strategic roadmap to fix them."
					}
				},
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "How long does the audit take?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "The full process takes about one week. It starts with a 30-minute strategy call, followed by a 90-minute deep-dive audit session. You receive your Revenue Leak Map and prioritized action plan within 3–5 business days after the audit session."
					}
				},
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "What kind of businesses benefit from this audit?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "The audit is designed for online businesses doing at least some revenue - coaches, course creators, SaaS founders, consultants, and e-commerce operators. If you have traffic and offers but feel like you should be earning more, the audit will show you exactly why and what to fix first."
					}
				},
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "What happens after the audit?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "You walk away with a complete Revenue Leak Map, a prioritized action plan, and a quick-win list you can implement immediately. If you want help executing the roadmap, you can upgrade to our Revenue Systems Consulting engagement - but there is zero pressure to do so."
					}
				}
			]
		})} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<!-- Hero -->
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-24 md:py-36">
			<div class="content-width">
				<div class="prose-width">
					<p class="fade-in mb-6 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Revenue Leak Audit</p>
					<h1 class="hero-headline fade-in fade-in-delay-1 font-display font-bold text-text">
						Find the Leaks in Your Business System
					</h1>
					<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
						Most online businesses are leaking revenue and don't even know it. Not because they lack traffic or offers - but because their system has invisible gaps. A broken funnel step here, a missing upsell there, a retention problem nobody measured. These leaks compound silently, costing thousands every month.
					</p>
					<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
						The Revenue Leak Audit is a complete diagnostic of your business's revenue pipeline. We map every stage - from how you acquire attention to how you monetize trust - and pinpoint exactly where the money is slipping through. No guesswork. No generic advice. Just a clear, prioritized map of what's broken and how to fix it.
					</p>
					<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
						This audit is for founders and operators who know they should be earning more from the traffic and customers they already have - and want a precise answer to the question: <em class="text-text">where is the revenue going?</em>
					</p>
					<div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-3 mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
						<a href={brand.strategyCall.checkoutUrl} class="cta-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							Book Strategy Call - €97
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
						</a>
						<p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-muted">30 Min | €97 | Payment at booking</p>
						<a href="/services/consulting" class="cta-ghost inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							See Consulting Services
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Background grid effect -->
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -z-10 h-[800px] w-[800px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,136,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
		</section>

		<!-- What the Audit Reveals -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">The Diagnostic</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					What the Audit Reveals
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					We don't just look at your analytics dashboard. We reverse-engineer your entire revenue flow and expose the gaps most businesses never see.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m16 12-4-4-4 4"/><path d="M12 16V8"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Traffic Leaks</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Are you attracting the right people - or burning budget on audiences that will never convert? We analyze traffic quality, source efficiency, and audience-offer alignment to find where attention is being wasted before it ever enters your funnel.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 2v7.527a2 2 0 0 1-.211.896L4.72 20.55a1 1 0 0 0 .9 1.45h12.76a1 1 0 0 0 .9-1.45l-5.069-10.127A2 2 0 0 1 14 9.527V2"/><path d="M8.5 2h7"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Funnel Gaps</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Every step in your funnel is a potential drop-off point. We map the full journey from first touch to purchase - identifying friction, missing steps, and broken transitions that are silently killing your conversion rate.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Conversion Killers</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">The moment of purchase is where most revenue dies. We audit your sales pages, checkout flows, objection handling, and social proof - the elements that turn interest into money. No trust signals, no testimonials, no sale.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Monetization Holes</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">You might be leaving 30–50% of your potential revenue on the table through missing upsells, underpriced offers, no order bumps, and zero backend monetization. We find every monetization opportunity your system is currently ignoring.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- What You Get -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Deliverables</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					What You Get
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					This isn't a vague report with generic recommendations. You get actionable, specific deliverables you can execute on immediately.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="uhl-card text-center">
						<div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="M12 18v-6"/><path d="m9 15 3-3 3 3"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Revenue Leak Map</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">A visual breakdown of your complete revenue pipeline showing exactly where money is leaking at each stage - with estimated revenue impact per leak.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card text-center">
						<div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.376 3.622a1 1 0 0 1 3.002 3.002L7.368 18.635a2 2 0 0 1-.855.506l-2.872.838a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.838-2.872a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.854z"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Prioritized Action Plan</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Not just what's broken - but what to fix first. Every leak is ranked by revenue impact and implementation effort so you know exactly where to start.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card text-center">
						<div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m3 8 4-4 4 4"/><path d="M7 4v16"/><path d="M11 12h4"/><path d="M11 16h7"/><path d="M11 20h10"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Quick Win List</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Immediate-impact changes you can implement in the first 48 hours. These are the low-hanging fixes that start recovering revenue before the bigger projects begin.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Who This Is For -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<div class="prose-width">
					<p class="mb-4 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Is This For You?</p>
					<h2 class="section-heading mb-10 font-display font-bold text-text">
						Who This Is For
					</h2>

					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Coaches & Consultants</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">You're getting clients but know your pipeline could be 2-3x more efficient. You want to stop relying on referrals alone and build a system that works while you sleep.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Course Creators</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">You've built the product but the sales page converts at 1% and you have no upsell path. The audit shows you where the 5x revenue multiplier is hiding in your existing funnel.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">SaaS Founders</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Churn is eating your growth. Your trial-to-paid conversion is below benchmark. You're spending more on acquisition than you're recovering in the first 6 months. The audit maps every leak in your SaaS revenue engine.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Digital Business Operators</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">E-commerce, membership sites, digital products - if you have traffic, offers, and transactions, the audit will find the revenue you're missing. Typical clients discover 20–40% untapped revenue potential.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The Process -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">How It Works</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					The Process
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					Three steps from blind spots to a clear action plan. The whole process takes about a week.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">01</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Strategy Call</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							30-minute strategy call (€97) where we learn about your business, revenue model, current challenges, and goals. We determine if the audit is the right fit - and what to focus the deep dive on.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">30 MINUTES &middot; €97</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">02</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Audit Session</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Deep-dive analysis of your complete revenue system. We walk through every stage together - traffic, offer, funnel, conversion, monetization, retention, and LTV - with live screen share and real-time diagnostics.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">90 MINUTES &middot; LIVE</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">03</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Report + Roadmap</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Within 3–5 business days, you receive your complete Revenue Leak Map, Prioritized Action Plan, and Quick Win List - ready to execute. We include a 30-minute follow-up call to walk through the findings.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">DELIVERED IN 3–5 DAYS</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pricing -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Investment</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					Choose Your Level
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					Start with a diagnostic, or go deeper with strategy and full implementation.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
					<!-- Audit -->
					<div class="group relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-accent/40 bg-bg2 p-10 shadow-[0_0_48px_rgba(0,255,136,0.06)] transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/60">
						<div class="mb-6">
							<div class="mb-1 flex items-center gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">The Audit</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark uppercase">Revenue Leak Analysis</p>
						</div>
						<p class="mb-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Complete diagnostic of your revenue system. You get a prioritized map of leaks, quick wins, and a roadmap for fixing them. Option to continue working together afterwards - no obligation.
						</p>
						<div class="mb-6 border-t border-border pt-6">
							<span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-text">1k &ndash; 2k</span>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-dark">One-time investment</p>
						</div>
						<ul class="mb-8 space-y-3 text-[15px] text-muted">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Full Revenue Leak Analysis (90 min)
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Revenue Leak Map (all 7 stages)
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Prioritized Action Plan + Quick Win List
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Written Report + Roadmap
							</li>
						</ul>
